summary.span: 提供靜態屬性，會傳回對應 Unicode 規格區塊的預先定義 執行個體。

span.span: Provides static properties that return predefined instances that correspond to blocks from the Unicode specification.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您使用屬性來擷取的 Unicode 具名範圍，其中每個連續的 Unicode 字碼指標的區塊所組成。You use properties to retrieve Unicode named ranges, each of which consists of a contiguous block of Unicode code points. 有些範圍會包含未定義的字碼指標。Some ranges include undefined code points. 例如，在**亞美尼亞文**Unicode 區塊 (U + 0530年-U + 058F)，U + 0530，U + 0557年-U + 0558，U + 0560，U + 0588，與 U + 058B-058 C 是未定義。For example, in the **Armenian** Unicode block (U+0530-U+058F), U+0530, U+0557-U+0558, U+0560, U+0588, and U+058B-058C are undefined. 在結尾的範圍，或任何位置之間的範圍的開頭，就會發生一或多個未定義的字碼指標。One or more undefined code points can occur at the beginning of a range, at the end of a range, or anywhere in between. 目前，類別僅具名範圍中基本多語文平面 (BMP)，其延伸了從 U + 0000 到 U + FFFF 的支援。Currently, the class supports only named ranges in the Basic Multilingual Plane (BMP), which extends from U+0000 to U+FFFF.
